[
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_1\\unordinary_ep1_p000.jpg",
    "text": "Two years ago, my father wrote a book"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_1\\unordinary_ep1_p001.jpg",
    "text": "It was about a man who lived amongst a world of € cripples.\nThis man, he used his ability only for others"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_1\\unordinary_ep1_p002.jpg",
    "text": "Helping the weak\nSaving Lives.\nSpreading wealth"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_1\\unordinary_ep1_p003.jpg",
    "text": ""
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_1\\unordinary_ep1_p004.jpg",
    "text": "Spoiler, he ends up dying -\nBut it wasn't sad, because he brought charity-"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_1\\unordinary_ep1_p005.jpg",
    "text": "And the world became peaceful"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_1\\unordinary_ep1_p006.jpg",
    "text": ""
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_1\\unordinary_ep1_p007.jpg",
    "text": "WORDINARY Story & Art by uru-chan"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_1\\unordinary_ep1_p008.jpg",
    "text": ""
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_1\\unordinary_ep1_p009.jpg",
    "text": "Wellston Private High School\nCafeteria"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_1\\unordinary_ep1_p010.jpg",
    "text": "The school's famous Triple Chocolate Cake is only served once a month\nAnd because this is such a rare event;\neveryone rushes to the cafe first thing during lunch time.\nIalways get there late because Im not asfast as everyone else_\nBut TODAY, Ihave a good feeling!"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_1\\unordinary_ep1_p011.jpg",
    "text": "Step away from that last slice?\nIcall dibs'"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_1\\unordinary_ep1_p012.jpg",
    "text": "Hey? Give that back, Arlo? Icalled that piece first!"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_1\\unordinary_ep1_p013.jpg",
    "text": "What? You \"called it\"? You should know how it works by now, Remi:\nIt's first come first serve: If you want a piece, you gotta be faster than that'\nBetter luck next time, shrimp:"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_1\\unordinary_ep1_p014.jpg",
    "text": "No way:"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_1\\unordinary_ep1_p015.jpg",
    "text": "Fve waited an entire month for that cake:\n[won't back down:\n2\n~"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_1\\unordinary_ep1_p016.jpg",
    "text": "Hand it over; jerk'"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_1\\unordinary_ep1_p017.jpg",
    "text": "Oh, so that's how you want to play?\nBring it on, little shrimp'"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_1\\unordinary_ep1_p018.jpg",
    "text": "Ohgod, those two are at it again _.\nReally? Ugh, here we go.\nHey, Ibet twenty bucks that Remi will win this round'"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_1\\unordinary_ep1_p019.jpg",
    "text": ""
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_1\\unordinary_ep1_p020.jpg",
    "text": "Great; theyre already fighting over the last piece."
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_1\\unordinary_ep1_p021.jpg",
    "text": "WHAT? MISSED IT AGAIN?!"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_1\\unordinary_ep1_p022.jpg",
    "text": "IlL never get a slice."
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_1\\unordinary_ep1_p023.jpg",
    "text": "WORDINARY"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_1\\unordinary_ep1_p024.jpg",
    "text": ""
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_1\\unordinary_ep1_p025.jpg",
    "text": "SUBSCRIBE for more sweetsi"
  },
